text: Šmartno v Tuhinju (; ) is a village in the Tuhinj Valley in the Municipality of Kamnik in the Upper Carniola region of Slovenia. ==Church== Saint Martin's Church The parish church in the village is dedicated to Saint Martin. ==References== ==External links== *Šmartno v Tuhinju at Geopedia * Category:Populated places in the Municipality of Kamnik
title: Šmartno v Tuhinju
